The paper introduces a new method for training neural networks using multilevel methods, which is a technique commonly used in numerical analysis and scientific computing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NA (Numerical Analysis), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
